      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# payment-terms model defines payment conditions and schedules\n\n`powerhouse/payment-terms` (16 ops) configures the conditions under which payments are expected \u2014 net terms, early payment discounts, late penalties. Applied to invoices and billing statements.\n\n## Position in Ecosystem\n\nFinance & Billing zone. Provides payment configuration that [[invoice model generates formal payment requests]] and [[billing-statement model captures periodic billing summaries]] consume.\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[ecosystem map]]\n- [[object relations]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:40.000Z"
